result.name: Yoshinoya

reviews.text: Poor service, bad aircon, wet floor and dirty place. The food was adequate but the service was extremely poor. I give this one star

Standard and an easy go to place for a quick curry rice dish. Nothing too special nor are the flavours unique. It is overall good tasting and a place to go when you want something quick. Pricing is average/low (dependent on what you get). Seating can be limited. Service is quick.
Bad service bad taste. I'm an Yoshinoya addict.
Eating hotpots in yoshinoya is good , when you eat together with your family and friends.
Typical fast food restaurant offering small meals at bargain price.
